Frankie Randall (singer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frankie_Randall_(singer) 0 Frankie Randall (born Franklin Joseph "Frank" Lisbona; January 11, 1938 – December 28, 2014) was an American singer, dancer, songwriter, vocalist, actor, and comedian. His acting credits include The Dean Martin Summer Show and Day of the Wolves.
